> Author: DevSkyy Enterprise Team
> Date: October 26, 2025
  
> Citation: NIST SP 800-38D (Recommendation for Block Cipher Modes of Operation:
> Galois/Counter Mode), published Dec 2007, reaffirmed 2024
> """
  
! import base64
